ie.gmit.dip

Class Mapper

  • java.lang.Object
    • ie.gmit.dip.Mapper
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMapper

    public class Mapper
extends java.lang.Object
implements IMapper
    A mapper that maps synonyms to common words using a hashmap. Each synonym has its own entry and the common word maps to itself. The mapper is case insensitive, i.e. both "Foo" and "foo" map to the same common word.
    Author:
    caoimhekilbride

      • getCommon

        public java.lang.String getCommon(java.lang.String word)
        Returns the common word that is synonym to the input. If a synonym does not exist, it returns null. The complexity is O(1).
